Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:23.73,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませてまで　笑えなくても
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.45,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そう言って彼女は　うつむいてたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:34.18,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}夜に泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:41.96,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷たく張り付いて凍えている
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:49.13,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}降り続く現実に傘などない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:55.70,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生きていく事が戦いなんて
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.30,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そんな理由だけで閉じ込められた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.27,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}マイハートマイストーリー
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:09.84,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪のムコウが見えるの　輝いている
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:16.53,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ちいさな窓には　あの頃みたいに　青い空がうつる
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:22.60,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ああ鳥のように飛べはしないけど
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:34.77,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}誰かを悲しませたとき感じる痛み
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:42.06,OP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}忘れないように　そっと目を閉じて　泣いた
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.24,0:03:23.73,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若能讓你忘卻傷痛 我寧願捨棄笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.74,0:03:27.45,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}如是言語的她 默然低下了頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.46,0:03:34.18,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}任憑淚水洗刷著夜色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.96,0:03:41.96,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷漠蔓延著凍結一切
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.20,0:03:49.13,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛這無可喘息的現實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.73,0:03:55.70,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}生存就是戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.71,0:03:59.30,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}被這可悲的理由束縛著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.31,0:04:02.27,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}My heart my story
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.39,0:04:09.84,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}淚水的彼岸 那閃耀的光芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.90,0:04:16.53,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}狹小的窗口中 滿眼是往昔的藍天
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:22.60,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}雖然無法像鳥兒一樣飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.36,0:04:34.77,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為讓悲傷永遠銘記於心而生的痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.81,0:04:42.06,OPcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}為了忘卻而閉目哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----ED
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:15.69,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}花は風に揺れ踊るように　雨は大地を潤すように
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:20.06,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}この世界は寄り添い合い　生きてるのに
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:31.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}なぜ人は傷付け合うの　なぜ別れは訪れるの
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:37.26,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君が遠くに行ってもまだ　いつもこの心の真ん中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.58,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}あの優しい笑顔で埋め尽くされたまま
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:50.74,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}抱きしめた君の欠片に　痛み感じてもまだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:54.52,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}繋がるから　信じてるよ　また逢えると
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.56,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:01.83,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:07.23,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}君の孤独を分けて欲しい
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:12.53,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you　I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.10,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}光でも闇でも
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:25.19,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}二人だから信じ合える
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:30.61,ED,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}NO 離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.19,0:21:15.69,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}如同花朵隨風起舞 如同雨水滋潤大地
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.69,0:21:20.06,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}這個世界如此緊密不分 如此活潑生機
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.17,0:21:31.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}卻為何人們要互相傷害 為何離別會突然降臨
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.81,0:21:37.26,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}即便去往遙遠的地方 你總是會活在我心底
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.31,0:21:41.58,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}那份溫柔的笑顏依舊映在眼裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.73,0:21:50.74,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}擁抱著你的碎片 刺痛著我的身體
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.74,0:21:54.52,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}但心心相連 因為我堅信 會再見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:56.56,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I am waiting for your love
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.56,0:22:01.83,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.93,0:22:07.23,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}多麼想分擔你的孤寂
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.36,0:22:12.53,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}I love you  I trust you
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.71,0:22:18.10,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}無論身處黑暗或是光明
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.16,0:22:25.19,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}只要在一起就可以相信
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.32,0:22:30.61,EDcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3\fad(200,200)}永遠不再分離
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,----Dialogue
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.97,0:00:03.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.37,0:00:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞·肖漢博格制造Gundam…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.23,0:00:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 制造GN-DRIVER的理由…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.64,0:00:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.38,0:00:15.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武力介入只是為此的布局
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.40,0:00:17.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊奧利亞的目的是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.15,0:00:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導人類的革新
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.70,0:00:23.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.05,0:00:25.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在變革之中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.94,0:00:27.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變革?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是你所領會到的極致嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.29,0:00:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者一定會再度…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.52,0:00:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到那時 請務必賜予我戰斗的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.29,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,復仇嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.83,0:00:51.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我所追求的是只有戰斗者才能到達的極致
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.27,0:00:58.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少年曾經對我說過 世界在扭曲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.69,0:01:03.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 對他而言 存在價值只有不停的戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:06.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.81,0:01:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是和你戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.96,0:01:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了那極致裡的勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.72,0:01:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你追求的只有勝利嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.65,0:01:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還有什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.62,0:01:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.12,0:01:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和未來相連的 明天!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:35.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,殺無赦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.02,0:01:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,空手奪白刃!?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.22,0:01:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的 戰斗!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.70,0:02:15.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰…戰斗吧 少年
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劈了我 將勝利握於手中
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.07,0:02:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.23,0:02:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼不殺我!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.22,0:02:34.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要活著
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.43,0:02:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活著迎接明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.25,0:02:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那才是我的戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.86,0:02:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙慈 露易絲·哈勒維的機體呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.34,0:02:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反應消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:56.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想是撤退了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.13,0:02:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.00,0:02:58.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.97,0:03:00.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為 為什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.84,0:03:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為純種覺醒了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.10,0:03:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.28,0:03:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是可以掌握人類命運的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.98,0:04:53.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說你知道維塔的所在了?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.06,0:04:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 王留美給的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.69,0:04:59.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到維塔了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.18,0:05:03.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號解析完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.59,0:05:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坐標是CZ9842R
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.62,0:05:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,米蕾娜
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:10.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用超長焦望遠鏡觀察該坐標
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.65,0:05:11.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.83,0:05:13.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉格朗日2…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.58,0:05:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連殖民地開發都沒有到過的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.28,0:05:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對藏東西而言 真是好地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.22,0:05:20.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在顯示目標地點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.13,0:05:23.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼都沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.34,0:05:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將這個區域的天體圖疊在這個畫面上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:27.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.81,0:05:31.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.31,0:05:34.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星星的位置偏離了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光學迷彩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.25,0:05:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特 算出存在偏移的范圍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.74,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.56,0:05:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,距離是…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.91,0:05:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直徑15公裡!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.35,0:05:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有15公裡!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.10,0:05:48.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼大的物體被隱藏起來了嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.66,0:05:50.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在月球的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.31,0:06:01.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯米拉琪小姐 收到實驗室運輸艦發來的暗號通訊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.82,0:06:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.64,0:06:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新裝備到了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.41,0:06:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,獨立治安維持部隊A-LAWS 將以全部兵力進行天行者的殲滅作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.67,0:06:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒作為反政府勢力的最終堡壘的他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.15,0:06:25.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏取統一世界的真正和平
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:28.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,期待諸位的勇猛表現
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.02,0:06:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,21艘巡洋艦和108架MS
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.50,0:06:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以如此規模戰力的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准將
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.29,0:06:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特許人士離開艦隊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.28,0:06:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隨他們去吧 戰場容不得他們隨意行動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.26,0:06:51.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯發出的返回命令
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.93,0:06:54.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他終於最好覺悟了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.32,0:06:56.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是 還在計劃之中哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.71,0:06:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為即將來臨之物日益迫近
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.86,0:07:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露易絲…哈勒維…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家人的仇? 我也有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.06,0:07:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別以為只有自己是不幸的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.15,0:07:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活該…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.93,0:07:31.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能過作為戰力的東西都帶過來了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.95,0:07:34.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam各機的活力加強組件
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.41,0:07:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有托勒密的補給
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.39,0:07:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連0-Gundam也帶來了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.94,0:07:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加上了粒子儲藏容器
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.98,0:07:44.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以能夠進行一定時間的戰斗哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.90,0:07:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 抓緊時間搬進去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在王留美指定的地點 艦隊正在集結
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會錯了 維塔就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:00.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有變革者的根據地
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.01,0:08:04.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突破A-LAW的艦隊 奪回維塔
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.80,0:08:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將是未曾有過的激戰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.82,0:08:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去 為了進行我自己的戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.18,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,庫洛斯洛特君…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.09,0:08:18.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定了 不會再迷茫了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.29,0:08:20.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我也參加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.66,0:08:26.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有這樣做的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.96,0:08:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算目的不同 我們都有前進理由
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.21,0:08:37.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 這種想法將於未來相連
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.67,0:08:44.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要為未來戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.92,0:08:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了解放變革者支配下的人類…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.09,0:08:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我和皮瑞斯這樣的人 不會再度出現在世界上…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.60,0:09:03.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒聯邦政府是我的任務
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.44,0:09:05.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狙擊變革者
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.86,0:09:06.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.33,0:09:09.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們要變革
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.28,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就無法迎接未來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.18,0:09:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.90,0:09:19.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,補給結束後 托勒密將起航
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.87,0:09:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.69,0:09:26.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 現在托勒密缺少舵手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.34,0:09:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是就在這裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.68,0:09:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拉塞!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:32.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能行嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.33,0:09:34.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.14,0:09:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.56,0:09:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到月亮的另一面
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.58,0:09:56.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑪麗娜公主 有好多星星啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.48,0:09:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢 非常漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.07,0:10:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.19,0:10:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都乖一點
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.41,0:10:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.90,0:10:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS正在拉格朗日2集結艦隊?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:18.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從G1那裡得到的情報哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天行者好像也打算到哪裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:24.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從政變派那裡也得到了同樣的情報
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.16,0:10:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還付了詳細的戰術計劃…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.88,0:10:35.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布置完畢了 大佐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.28,0:10:43.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於 審判降臨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.28,0:10:48.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是由作為純種而變革的剎那·F·塞艾 還是由我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.05,0:10:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來決定人類的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:54.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.05,0:11:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是為了尋找死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.70,0:11:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了生存而戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.37,0:11:19.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂武士道…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.88,0:11:27.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超望遠光學攝像頭 捕捉到敵方艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全員 一級戰斗准備
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.54,0:11:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.70,0:11:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菲露特…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.53,0:11:40.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個給你…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.60,0:11:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.82,0:11:45.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,琳達小姐在實驗室種出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.77,0:11:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要… 送給你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.37,0:11:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你 菲露特
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.99,0:11:54.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓瑪麗娜小姐不高興的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.72,0:11:57.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和她不是那種關系
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.05,0:11:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去Gundam那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.04,0:11:59.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.25,0:12:02.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要死啊! 剎那
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.90,0:12:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.36,0:12:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,托勒密號 全甲板打開
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.20,0:12:17.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都要將維塔奪回來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.74,0:12:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,引導我吧… 洛克昂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.48,0:12:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛德先生 期待你的戰果的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.80,0:12:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.82,0:12:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Seravee 提艾利亞·愛德
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.46,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准備好了麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.46,0:12:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.88,0:12:35.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫瑪麗也行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.80,0:12:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒!?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:39.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想那麼叫的話 就那麼叫好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.83,0:12:41.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.31,0:12:42.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.20,0:12:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Archer Arios
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.36,0:12:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雷魯亞·哈普狄斯姆
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.41,0:12:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,索瑪·皮瑞斯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.51,0:12:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向目標進發
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.57,0:12:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 出擊准備完成的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.29,0:13:00.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾紐 看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.00,0:13:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Cherudim 洛克昂·斯特拉特斯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.06,0:13:03.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彈無虛發!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.12,0:13:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的沒問題麼? 沙慈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.88,0:13:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擔心我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.84,0:13:17.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是我 也想要找到未來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.35,0:13:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.47,0:13:22.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 剎那·F·塞艾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.63,0:13:23.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.73,0:13:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser 沙慈·庫洛斯洛特
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.54,0:13:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發射!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.38,0:13:32.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈羅
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.15,0:13:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.12,0:13:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,0 Raiser DOCKING-MODE
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.33,0:13:50.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gundam從太空艦出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先遣部隊 攻擊開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.31,0:13:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特別任務艦 給我好好干哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.08,0:14:03.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牽制敵方部隊!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.88,0:14:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊～!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,壓縮粒子 完全解放!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.99,0:14:51.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺可以啊 這新裝備!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.71,0:15:02.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事!? 敵艦竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.32,0:15:06.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵艦 沒有減速的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.31,0:15:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自殺攻擊!?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.02,0:15:14.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 用RAISER SWORD對付敵方艦隊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.38,0:15:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:17.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,RAISER系統 啟動
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.79,0:15:21.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,TRANS-AM RAISER!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子干擾麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.38,0:15:55.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反相力場在廣域內展開的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.49,0:15:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子射線的效果下降
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.32,0:15:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陷阱麼!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.57,0:16:01.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒在至近距離展開已經不錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.27,0:16:03.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變更軌道 脫離這個力場!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.45,0:16:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比想象中對應得還早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.88,0:16:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,主力部隊 攻擊開始
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.69,0:16:14.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用數量壓倒他們!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.61,0:16:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剎那 粒子光束竟然!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.40,0:16:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.11,0:16:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,導彈的殘彈已經!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.12,0:16:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人的數量多過頭了!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.04,0:16:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.63,0:17:03.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提艾利亞!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.10,0:17:09.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被突破了!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.85,0:17:27.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷中彈!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.56,0:17:29.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,損傷情況…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.96,0:17:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 想一點點玩死我們麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.55,0:17:56.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵機 接近的說!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.49,0:18:11.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯… 什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.84,0:18:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.98,0:18:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.79,0:18:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護天行者組織!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.37,0:18:32.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,援軍!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.26,0:18:34.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.11,0:18:37.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.58,0:18:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來得真是時候!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.46,0:18:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,KATARON的武裝…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.49,0:18:49.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測到了反相力場?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.62,0:18:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.83,0:18:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將托勒密號沖向敵方艦隊!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.10,0:18:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼 竟然是KATARON?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.75,0:18:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就他們那點戰力…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.88,0:19:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准將 我方的運輸艦被!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:01.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,運輸艦又怎麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.91,0:19:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粒子光束來了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:03.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.96,0:19:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勸告A-LAWS部隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.38,0:19:18.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等揭竿而起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為聯邦執行惡政的傀儡的A-LAWS
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.93,0:19:23.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經無法稱為軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.13,0:19:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界發展的方向
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有通過全體人民的意見才可決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.07,0:19:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我等會對你們野蠻的行為定罪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.81,0:19:33.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而行正義與否將由市民決定
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.80,0:19:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那只可惡的女狐狸…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.70,0:19:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我打!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.65,0:19:43.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們是反政府勢力!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.60,0:19:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.23,0:19:50.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵方部隊接近過來了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.00,0:19:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MS部隊 攻擊開始!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.20,0:19:57.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死身的克拉薩瓦～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.55,0:20:00.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此上陣～!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過對些運輸艦你們在干什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.83,0:20:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們藏在僚艦的背後 無法攻擊!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.27,0:20:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的友軍不要理會
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.33,0:20:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和敵人一起給我擊落!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.58,0:20:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有我方的士兵在!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.51,0:20:26.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別囉嗦 我說了打!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.59,0:20:29.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,准將! 敵艦突破了反相力場!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.44,0:20:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說什麼!?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.06,0:20:36.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,G…Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.10,0:20:38.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,00 Raiser
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.40,0:20:40.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,驅逐目標!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.16,0:20:45.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我想點辦法啊～!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.13,0:22:38.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇～好厲害!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.49,0:22:41.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這會兒克勞斯他們已經加入了戰斗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.36,0:22:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰爭的… 光芒…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.47,0:22:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A-LAWS艦隊被突破了麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.02,0:22:53.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類看來還真是喜歡戰斗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.20,0:22:57.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是你讓他們這麼做的麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.03,0:23:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他們引導到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.28,0:23:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那應該也是你的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.84,0:23:04.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.86,0:23:10.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是比你們更上位種的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.27,0:23:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以說是創造神
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.45,0:23:14.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.10,0:23:17.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被野心支配的你的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.14,0:23:21.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通過腦量子波我可知道得一清二楚哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.46,0:23:27.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真遺憾啊 裡傑諾·瑞婕塔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.46,0:23:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡本斯·阿爾馬克!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.09,0:23:47.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.92,0:23:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.29,0:23:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會引導人類的 是我…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.24,0:23:56.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裡傑諾·瑞婕塔!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.19,0:24:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終於現出身姿的變革者的大型母艦
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.15,0:24:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在它面前的機師們有勝算麼
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.52,0:24:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:09.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生命之華彩
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.95,0:24:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凡光芒閃過之處 便有生命隕落…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:10.87,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}残された夢のあと　踏みつける
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.99,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}気まぐれな死神が立ち止まった
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:20.85,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すれ違う僕を見る冷たく 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.75,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}愚かな罪をけしかけるように
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:31.03,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}伸ばされた手をふりほどいた
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:36.26,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}反逆のシナリオに舞い降りた堕天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:42.63,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なぜ君は光の外にいるのか　気づいたよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:50.39,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}もし僕じゃなく生まれたら　笑っていられたかな
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:57.21,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無償の愛その中で　孤独など知らぬまま
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:07.34,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}郷愁を映し出す　遠い空を見つめた
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:19.05,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんなに願っても永久に触れられない
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:26.13,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}負けていたんだ　自分の闇に
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:33.32,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}奪われた儚き光　生きる証をつないで
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:37.35,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どんな運命も受け入れて
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:42.31,IN2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕は生きる　最後の瞬間まで
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.90,0:12:10.87,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}踐踏著 殘留的夢的痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.97,0:12:15.99,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}隨心所欲的死神佇立著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.04,0:12:20.85,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}冷冷地注視擦身而過的我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.86,0:12:25.75,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}仿佛正在慫恿我犯下愚蠢的罪行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:31.03,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}甩開他伸出的手臂
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.26,0:12:36.26,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}叛逆的劇本裡 飄落下墮落的天使
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.34,0:12:42.63,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我已經知曉 為何你身處光芒之外
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.63,0:12:50.39,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}倘若我不是作為我降臨人世的話 是否就能一直笑逐顏開呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.50,0:12:57.21,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}深陷毫無回報的愛中 孤獨什麼的我一概不知
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.45,0:13:07.34,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我一直凝望著 映照出鄉愁的遙遠的天空
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.44,0:13:19.05,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無論再怎麼許願 那份永遠還是遙不可及
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.96,0:13:26.13,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我敗給了 我自己的陰暗面
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.13,0:13:33.32,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}所掠奪的幻滅的光芒 維系著我生存過的證明
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.46,0:13:37.35,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}無論怎樣的命運 我都會接受
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.35,0:13:42.31,IN2cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我要生存下去 直到最後一刻


